title: BACKUP Utilization Dashboard

widgets.title: Users with Activities This Month
How many learners use the platform on average, by course?
widgets.desc: The dynamic chart represents data pertaining to enrollments and scoped to the level of permission for your account. Interact with and utilize this dashboard to analyze users.

widgets.title: How many learners use the platform, (in aggregate)?
widgets.desc: The dynamic chart represents data pertaining to new and active users, presented in aggregate, and scoped to the level of permission for your account.

widgets.title: Are learners happy with the platform?
widgets.desc: The dynamic chart represents data pertaining to review score, presented as an average, and scoped to the level of permission for your account. Interact with and utilize this dashboard to analyze learner satisfaction with the platform.

widgets.title: How often do learners study?
widgets.desc: The dynamic chart represents data pertaining to users, presented in as an average, and scoped to the level of permission for your account. Interact with and utilize this dashboard to analyze the average sessions per user as well as the average session duration .

widgets.title: How many exams do learners take?
widgets.desc: The dynamic chart represents data pertaining to courses, presented in aggregate, and scoped to the level of permission for your account. Interact with and utilize this dashboard to analyze the total number of exams started and completed each month.

widgets.title: How long do learners spend studying?
widgets.desc: The dynamic chart represents data pertaining to users, presented in as an average, and scoped to the level of permission for your account. Interact with and utilize this dashboard to analyze the average amount of time users spend on the platform .

widgets.title: How are learners spending their time?
widgets.desc: The dynamic chart represents data pertaining to users, presented as a total percentage, and scoped to the level of permission for your account. Interact with and utilize this dashboard to analyze how platform users are spending their time (in hours).

widgets.title: Does learner performance aligned with perceived confidence?
widgets.desc: The dynamic table represents data pertaining to course question categories showing perceived confidence against actual performance.

widgets.title: How do learners score on exams?
widgets.desc: The dynamic chart represents data pertaining to courses, presented as an average, and scoped to the level of permission for your account. Interact with and utilize this dashboard to analyze the total number of exams completed (by pass/fail) and the average exam score for users.

widgets.title: How many users have licenses?
widgets.desc: The dynamic chart represents data pertaining to users and is scoped to the level of permission for your account. Interact with and utilize this dashboard to analyze the number of licenses users have.

widgets.title: Does device type affect learner engagement?
widgets.desc: The dynamic chart represents data pertaining to users, presented as a total percentage, and scoped to the level of permission for your account. Interact with and utilize this dashboard to analyze the percentage of all user study hours composed of resources by device type. ("Other" includes, but not limited to, discussions, messages and study plan review)

widgets.title: Which question topics do learners study the most?
widgets.desc: The dynamic chart represents data pertaining to courses and users, presented as an average, and scoped to the level of permission for your account. Interact with and utilize this dashboard to analyze relative usage, by average answers per question in each category rather than total answer.

widgets.title: Are learners likely to recommend the course to others?
widgets.desc: The dynamic chart represents data pertaining to NPS (net promoter score - industry standard), presented in aggregate, and scoped to the level of permission for your account. Interact with and utilize this dashboard to analyze learners who answer the question "How likely are you to recommend your course to a friend".

widgets.title: How many users have logged in?
widgets.desc: The dynamic chart represents login data pertaining to users and scoped to the level of permission for your account. Interact with this dashboard to analyze monthly logins.

content.html: This dynamic and interactive dashboard presents timely data pertaining to end user utilization at the tenant level - in aggregate and in relation to specific learning activities, locations, and more - scoped to the level of permission for your account.  Info

widgets.title: Which device do learners use to study?
widgets.desc: The dynamic chart represents data pertaining to users, presented as a total percentage, and scoped to the level of permission for your account. Interact with and utilize this dashboard to analyze the different device types users leverage while studying on the platform.

widgets.title: With which exam questions do learners struggle?
widgets.desc: The dynamic scatterplot represents data pertaining to courses, presented as an average percentage, and scoped to the level of permission for your account. Interact with and utilize this dashboard to analyze the average percent correct for exam questions against the average time taken to answer each question.

widgets.title: Which exam topics take learners the longest?
widgets.desc: The dynamic boxplot represents data pertaining to courses, presented in aggregate, and scoped to the level of permission for your account. Interact with and utilize this dashboard to analyze the distribution of time taken on exam questions by topic.

widgets.title: Are learners retained over time?
widgets.desc: The dynamic heat map represents data pertaining to users, presented as a percentage, and scoped to the level of permission for your account. Interact with and utilize this dashboard to analyze user retention over time (each square indicates the percentage of users with an activity completed in the month indicated on the y-axis, who registered an activity in the range shown on the x-axis).

widgets.title: How many learners use the platform per course per month?
widgets.desc: The dynamic table represents data pertaining to learner usage by course. You can use this raw table for any CSV export needs.

widgets.title: Which lesson topics do learners study the most?
widgets.desc: The dynamic chart represents data pertaining to users, presented as an average, and scoped to the level of permission for your account. Interact with and utilize this dashboard to analyze relative usage, by average confidence levels by lesson rather than total usage.
